# NextAct

- Modular monolith: domain code in `src/features/*`, secrets/AI in `src/server/*`.
- Do not number `src`, `public`, or `supabase`. Numbers are for `docs/` only.
- Never put service role or AI keys in client code.
- All model calls go through `src/server/ai` gateway.
- Banned copy: "quiet" and U+2014 em dash.
- Prefer updating the matching doc under `docs/` when behavior changes.
